      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Back of Envelope Calculations\n\n- 1 billion DAU\n- Average user click 1 ad per day\n- 1 billion daily events. 100k seconds in one day, so 10k\nevents per second\n- Assume an event is 0.1 kb, so we need 100GB\nstorage daily",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Back of Envelope Calculations\n\n- 1 billion DAU\n- Average user click 1 ad per day\n- 1 billion daily events. 100k seconds in one day, so 10k events per second\n- Assume an event is 0.1 kb, so we need 100GB storage daily",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
